# .env.example — SuperCoach-VIA configuration overrides
# ======================================================
#
# Copy this file to `.env` at the repo root to override the defaults baked into
# config.py. `.env` is gitignored, so your local overrides are never committed.
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# HOW IT WORKS (zero dependencies — config.py has a built-in parser, no
# python-dotenv needed):
#
#   Precedence, lowest to highest:
#     1. Defaults hard-coded in config.py
#     2. Values in this .env file
#     3. Real environment variables (export FOO=bar) — these always win
#
# FILE FORMAT:
#   - KEY=VALUE, one per line.
#   - Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#   - A leading `export ` is allowed and stripped: `export KEY=value` works.
#   - Surrounding single or double quotes around a value are stripped.
#   - No variable interpolation, no multiline values, no inline-comment
#     stripping (a '#' inside a value is treated literally, so paths with '#'
#     survive intact).
#
# All keys are OPTIONAL. Anything you leave out falls back to the config.py
# default shown in the comment beside it.

# --- Filesystem ------------------------------------------------------------

# Absolute path to the repo root. If unset, config.py auto-detects it from its
# own location, so you usually do NOT need this. Set it only if you import
# config.py from an unusual working directory or a relocated checkout.
# SUPERCOACH_REPO_ROOT=/home/abhi/git/SuperCoach-VIA

# --- Season ----------------------------------------------------------------

# The active season that season-specific docs (afl-*-<year>.md) target, and the
# season named in fixed output filenames/titles. Most analysis scripts still
# auto-detect the current season from the freshest data row; this only affects
# the places that hard-name a season. Default: 2026.
# SUPERCOACH_SEASON_YEAR=2026

# AFL home-and-away season length (games each team plays). Default: 22.
# SUPERCOACH_HOME_AND_AWAY_GAMES=22

# --- Data refresh ----------------------------------------------------------

# Players with any game on/after this date are re-scraped on a delta refresh
# (avoids re-fetching ~12,500 stable retired-player files). Default: 2024-01-01.
# SUPERCOACH_ACTIVE_SINCE=2024-01-01
